data.description: Large 3 bedroom 2 bath home in Waiehu Heights. Wonderful views of West Maui Mountains, Haleakala and the ocean. Step out to the yard, which has  beautiful views and space for enjoying the fresh air and sunshine. This home is  ready for a new owner and refresh. The layout features a large kitchen with open concept and lots of natural lighting. All three bedrooms upstairs are spacious. The lower level of the house has a separate laundry area, additional full bath and large bonus room with entry to the garage. This is a house that is able to accommodate a larger family and could possibly be configured for two living areas. This is a potential short sale and subject to court approval and probate process.
